title: Looking for high gold + Top or jungle
body:
Chasing another player for our ranked 5s team full of mostly plat players.

Needs to be on most nights and playing til late.

replies.body: I'm keen to play top. Add me on league and let's chat.
Jg Main not gold atm but if you want to give me a trial its upto you
ill try out if all good

I can both jungle and support well,I was Plat 2 at the end of last season,
My placements didn't go as well as i planned and i am now Silver 1 but i plan to be back in plat soon..
I have been looking for a team environment 'where i can enjoy the game in its best form, i have played in ranked teams before and even on the CG ladder sometime in season 2 :)
Jungle Pref but support is my second best
